data.description: Welcome home to beautiful Shoreland! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house offers ample living space. The main floor features a cozy living room with a fireplace. Large kitchen and Dining Room. Lounge in the large sunroom and enjoy the natural light and the beauty of the outdoors from the comfort of your own home. Upstairs, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms, ensuring space for all. The basement offers additional living space that can be customized to suit your needs. Brand new roof, gutters and skylights Feb 2024. Don't miss your chance to make this wonderful property your own!
